{"type": "article", "id": 50795, "title": "阿迪达斯收入超 200 亿欧元，以及，OFF-WHITE 和 Byredo 合作款发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-03-05T03:50:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 41426, "name": "Byredo"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 43320, "name": "Off-White"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 1780, "name": "CK"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 2138, "name": "范冰冰"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180305114246RX625YA8BMNLQsvU.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/adidas-ceo/adidas-ceo-says-sales-grew-15-20-pct-in-2017-idUSL8N1QI34O\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>阿迪达斯去年销售额超过 200 亿欧元，商标侵权案获胜</strong></a> | 上周，阿迪达斯 CEO Kasper Rorsted 表示，受大中华地区、北美地区和电商推动，去年集团收入超过 200 亿欧元，增幅达到 15%－20%。最近关于阿迪达斯的商标侵权案也有了结果，欧盟法院宣布，禁止比利时制鞋公司 Shoe Branding 使用与阿迪达斯相似的“三条杠”进行注册，以免消费者混淆。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/japanese-retailers-mixed-sales-february-1202607014/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>受寒冷天气影响，迅销集团二月份同店销售额上涨 5.1%</strong></a> | 日本迅销集团上周五表示，受寒冷天气影响，迅销在日本的同店销售额上涨 5.1%，会员数上涨了 0.2%，客单购买量上涨了 4.8%。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.linkshop.com.cn/web/archives/2018/397709.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>范冰冰自创美容品牌 FANBEAUTY</strong></a> | 日前，范冰冰自创的美容品牌 FANBEAUTY 诞生，并同时在天猫上开设了官方旗舰店。目前所售的产品只有 FANBEAUTY UP 家用脸部射频电子美容仪<strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>范冰冰童颜机</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>这一款，销售页面显示，这款美容仪定价 3299 元，预售价格 2399 元，需支付 200 元定金，限量 1000 支，将于 3 月 25 日发货。欧睿咨询数据显示，美容仪在 2014 年全网销售就超过了 7500 万台，预计在 2020 年，全球美容仪市场将达到 3000 亿元人民币。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>3 月 2 日，<a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Calvin-Klein-205W39NYC-opens-Paris-headquarters,953966.html#.Wpyo2xNuYzU\" rel=\"nofollow\">Calvin Klein 205W39NYC </a>在巴黎 Rive Gauche 开设新总部。该总部也是 Calvin Klein 205W39NYC 进军欧洲市场的首个中心，它占地约 1500 平米，由 Raf Simons 和艺术家 Sterling Ruby 合作设计，内部挂了不少艺术装置的挑高空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113101QYzdsX7TChVN3SMl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.795385\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113101jukPyQZg8lWsY2Tf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670769\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113048VKUOqZzsic7JW0Fn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051130504MarZPoGAeSJL3w0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113051S7DylIQMNjtAvVxc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113051Xmibx2fRhd7Zj5c1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113053XWyY71LRmZHiuDcn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/adidas-skateboarding-na-kel-smith-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 发布职业车手 Na-kel Smith 的首波联名款</a>，包括 T 恤、连帽衫、运动裤等多款单品，鞋子还蛮好看的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113157nZJd7493r5BKhOac.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113158bvA9Depa4S0VXuHJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030511315789r2fyClIs0axLtB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113157csg8tBJ0aj3nGiF1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113157cEy9bwGsuZqtaxR5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>OFF-WHITE 和香氛品牌 Byredo 合作系列完整发布，取名<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/3/off-white-byredo-elevator-music-release-virgil-abloh-perfume-bags\" rel=\"nofollow\">“Elevator Music”</a>。 </p><p>该系列包括香水、头发香水和护手霜，还有手袋、牛仔外套，将从 4 月 23 日起至 5 月 7 日，在 Selfridges 和 Barneys Madison 发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113229kltRqxZWuQzhUnd0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113230xELJBRa1YjX0vHpr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113229nEWzAIV35BwObTGy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113229IE1Pt8rKS7ZdGB5N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051132286hpKuGnE4IF5jr8e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113228JF5qmBYh6dWnkwzO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030511322836nhaMEDWSwGUC8O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051132286ZqErWTUlVxk91y0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113228hSvCQlaFMm9OUn6s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113234gudGyOhMtlieRUz0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>和去年一样，今年夏天优衣库也找了一个主题在全世界范围内发起 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/uniqlo-ut-marvel-t-shirt-collection/#slide-13\" rel=\"nofollow\">UT 设计比赛</a>。 </p><p>今年的主题变成了漫威，共收到了 8500 多份参赛设计作品，先来看看部分被选中的设计，完整系列将在 4 月 26 日正式发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113324DwtQ0SVW2naGioOh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113323vQYqCU6spwmDRobt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113324h5UN1xzWAwoJvnXu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113324rJ4nty6gaHI3hlpR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113324wPReUruBjVlkWO63.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113325IiJLqbdrBD5GpROk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051133255z0jxANe87hPZ1c4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113325rfueoLRUG9ODMF6t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113326UF5dXRvlIjESNQ1Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113326xOIpiMNnsdLPajw6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051133269aX4SwYUxNu8nE5t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051133270wuIz5hqjOcgvVYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113327abKqXFQg0LUTDwpE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051133275JS3zfe6lEB1Nuht.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051133277dFliKgMSBe5T2p4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>近日的巴黎时装周看点颇多。<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/comme-des-garcons-fw18-nike-cortez/#slide-12\" rel=\"nofollow\">COMME des GARÇONS </a>把 Nike 阿甘鞋带上了秀场，但被改造成了厚底松糕版。模特们的着装看起来错综复杂——红色薄纱裙上衔接着不对称的紧身胸衣裙，层层叠叠不同布料的拼合，毛衣和纱裙的混搭...</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113411Gju8b0JeERKoNzP2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051134098gNt7JGxu3qdZiIs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113409uNHoznjmiQ5wX3EF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113410hmJ6HEsFdBtSIlMn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113411vH0AEyzmoLJF9TXd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113405J9mzeS7M20VPOfEb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113406EFkMTaixIuQnYR45.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113407rHNqhFLMnQcOIu8W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113407uaZ4jh9Ms1WF2kcO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113408IfltCPbmcRyZWXag.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113410ncqBEgY0y3lu29mK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051134117d9NCR5yihVPFBpc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/givenchy/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Givenchy </a>的设计师 Clare Waight Keller 说，自己这一季的创作灵感，是在看完电影《The Hunger》和纪录片《B-Movie: Lust &amp; Sound in West Berlin》之后产生的。 </p><p>Clare Waight Keller 似乎成功避免了时装周秀场上 80 年代的那一套陈词滥调，但同时，这一季没能制造出什么惊喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113536Q8FV4fOURYwxPpIs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113538VlO24hDBPxdCsGnc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113540F2p7OCf8WqxJXevS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113540cbzUgLNsHrwA6lM7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113541VUFRY50xO38h4LAD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113542MOVHdIKTmQLFx590.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113543Hpgc7vdxyPCJ3b0B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113544geKNZIRvTWdCObBm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030511354493qAogE0Vb1U8YSL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113545DNhGUzPXCeOVcjJR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113546ZGa6MpghlNTdcuve.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051135479nS8IFJsXMHVuBmD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113548N3p7wsUegvljfnti.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051135486RLezlt2O5jXUo8J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113548m2xGZa8XfRYIndvb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051135491LHrvbql6DuW2nRM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051135521MF8HfeaE9bRtonU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113552swdk4ZFWlzBtEm27.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113552PCsfiEkzlIgunWaR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113553Sdixs64CmIvUporf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113553Oj8w3PaRfxNzk4EF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305113554hkzN